{"tid":1918994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇網媒winandmac屌人唔like自己個page?","createTime":"2020-03-10T13:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T13:08:39.000Z","uid":75028,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1432470d0d40456572f5599a76ca862fd4d4f6f0","tid":1918994,"uid":75028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3393251527368445&amp;id=121622707864693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3393251527368445%26id%3D121622707864693&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=9bffa4f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3393251527368445&amp;id=121622707864693</a><br />\n今日見到人share呢個page出嚟<br />\n話無人留意 希望有人like<br />\n本來覺得黃媒要支持下<br />\n但入到去見到好多都係repost既野<br />\n又或者係主流傳媒有post過既野<br />\n甚至有啲Content farm感覺<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題係成日覺得懷才不遇<br />\n有啲post無乜人覆/like/唔肯share<br />\n個page就會屌9人<br />\n講到好似唔like就拖垮成場運動咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RwyusL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RwyusL.png&h=798cdc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PeUDFzo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPeUDFzo.png&h=215fd5dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXN5403.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXN5403.png&h=abfcb8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLAGDk4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLAGDk4.png&h=1b3f6705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明做傳媒好辛苦 付出同成果唔成正比<br />\n但當個page hit唔起<br />\n點解會係audiences既錯？<br />\n唔係應該反思下自己個page既質素咩？<br />\n<br />\n立場都撈咗好多年先成為主流 <br />\n個媒體有質素自然有人睇<br />\n<br />\n利申先 唔係分化 唔同意既可以入去like下個page 然後由我呢個post沉 不過我係想講 黃只係一個最低既門檻 喺黃圈入面可以再選擇自己覺得高質既野 而唔係見到黃 就好似老鳳咁捧紅 咁樣個黃圈先自可以持續做落去"},{"pid":"d33fd839b564f61d6bdbb2e7998a87affbc517